  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "WCW: The Main Event is a professional wrestling video game. Choose your fighters among top-ranked superstars. Each wrestler has his unique special move along with punch, clothesline, bodyslam, suplex, dropkick, and cross body block. Use your unique abilities to fight in one of two match types to maybe even throw one's opponent out of the ring!",
